Quang sat nhap khau vao Trung Quoc se tang 7,5 %
Nguyen nhan do nhu cau thep cho cac cong trinh xay dung nha o co so ha tang va san xuat may moc Trung Quoc tang
Cong hoi Hang hai quoc te va vung Baltic BIMCO to chuc hang hai lon nhat the gioi du bao nhap khau quang sat Trung Quoc se tang truong o muc 7,5 % trong nam 2013 tang so voi 6,4 % nam nay
Nhu cau nhap khau tang dong nghia voi viec se can nhieu hon cac tau cho lon de van chuyen hang hoa BIMCO cho biet trong mot bao cao dua ra hom thu tu.Trong thang 9 Trung Quoc nhap khau 65 trieu tan quang sat nhieu nhat ke tu thang 1/2011 chi ra rang nhu cau cua nuoc nay van tiep tuc tang len.Theo Gafin
Dau tram Loc Thuy chi ban cai danh
Chai dau tram 120ml gia 10.000-12.000 dong trong khi gia chai het mot nua
Dau tram nguyen chat khong the re nhu the
Lang dau tram Loc Thuy huyen Phu Loc Thua Thien-Hue da ton tai hon 100 nam ai den Hue cung muon mua dau ve lam qua
Nhung vi ly do kinh te hien da so nhung ho ban dau tram o day deu nhap dau tu noi khac dua ve.Ven theo quoc lo 1A doan qua doc deo Phuoc Tuong hon 40 lo dau tram nghi ngut khoi ben canh la trung day dau tram voi cac bang hieu dau tram Loc Thuy dau tram nguyen chat dau tram loai I ... Nhung dang sau nhung bang hieu ay la dieu khong phai ai cung biet
Tai lang lo dau tram lon nhat la lo Thanh Binh- noi duy nhat cua lang nghe co dang ky nhan hieu co phieu kiem nghiem va duoc bau chon la san pham cong nghiep nong thon tieu bieu cap huyen nam 2011
Tai lo ben canh nhung chai dau mang thuong hieu Thanh Binh thi co mot goc trung bay nhung chai dau khong ro nguon goc de khach hang phan biet that gia
Nhung that bat ngo theo loi ong chu lo Mai Dinh Hung thi nhung chai dau hieu Thanh Binh cung khong phai cua lo ma cung la dau nhap va dan nhan Thanh Binh
Khi hoi dau nguyen chat do lo nau thi ong Hung moi vao nha lay dau that ra
“Khach di ngang day chi biet o day nau dau tram ban thoi con hiem nguoi biet dau tot dau xau
Nhieu nguoi lan dau moi biet mui dau tram thi lam sao phan biet duoc
Ma khach di duong thi cung chi mua duoc lan thoi ” ong Mai Dinh Hung thu thuc.Sang lo dau cua chi Le Thi Tam
Hai vo chong chi dang chuan bi cho ra lo mot me dau moi
Vo chong chi Tam khang dinh “O day khong co co so nao ban dau that 100 %
Da so ho deu ban cai danh dau tram Loc Thuy ma thoi
Lo toi ai thich re thi toi ban dau khong ro nguon goc thich dat thi ban dau nguyen chat do toi nau ”
Nhung cua tiem khac tuy lo van do nghi ngut mui dau tram van ngao ngat nhung khi hoi mua nhung nguoi nay cung dem ra nhung chai dau khong ro nguon goc nhap tu nhung noi khac ve de ban
Khach hang kho co the phan biet tot xau khi thay lo van do lua va dau van dang chay duoc ben canh nhung chai dau
Hau nhu cac cua tiem tren dia ban xa Thuy Loc chi biet lay dau va ban chu ban than ho khong he biet dau nay xuat xu o dau
“Toi ban thi ban cho co biet no tu mo ve dau ” ong Nguyen Van Tien chu mot lo dau o day cho biet
Qua tim hieu o day co hai cua tiem My Hoa va Hoa Suong la hai dai ly cua loai dau nay muon lay bao nhieu cung co
Chi Hoa chu tiem dau My Hoa cho biet “Toi mua can ve roi ra chai ban cho cac cua tiem khac
Dau nay duoc lay o cho Dong Ba goc tich thi khong biet cho nao ve
Dau nay thi chi ban khach du lich thoi
Khach Thai Lan mua nhieu lam ”
Theo chi dan cua chi Hoa phong vien gap duoc chi Be Tho la mot trong nhung noi cung cap dau tram lon nhat tren dia ban tinh Thua Thien-Hue
Theo chi Tho toan bo duoi Loc Thuy va gan 10 cua tiem o cho Dong Ba deu lay dau o co so cua chi
Chi bo day du cac loai dau tram tu tot den xau nhung da so khach chi deu lay hang dom de ban
“Co so cua toi cung cap ca nuoc chu khong rieng chi o Hue
Co so toi co hang tram nguoi nau trong rung o tren Tay Nguyen
Mot ngay toi ban hang nghin lit dau dom
Nguoi ta mua ve thich thi ho dan hieu ho vao ” ong chu cua hang Be Tho noi.Niem tin cua khach hang vao lang dau tren tram tuoi dang bi mat dan vi mua phai hang dom
Theo ba Tran Thi Quyen 61 tuoi mot nguoi da nau dau hon 40 nam nay cho biet “Dau tram nguyen chat khong the re nhu the
Mot chai 120ml chi co gia 10 nghin -12 nghin dong trong khi gia chiec chai het 5 nghin ruoi
Thi toi cung khong biet dau do la dau gi ”.Dau tram la loai dau gio chiet xuat tu tinh dau cua cay tram co huong thom va mui vi de chiu duoc dung trong nhieu loai thuoc ho nuoc suc mieng thuoc sat khuan phong ngua cam mao giam cac con dau o khop tay chan tri cac vet con trung can lam da sung va ngua cac van de ve da nhu viem da chay nang phat ban ... cho nguoi gia nguoi benh san phu tre em ke ca tre so sinh
Nam 2008 nghien cuu cua OPODIS pharma thuc hien tai Vien Pasteur TP HCM cho thay dau thuoc su dung α-Terpineol chiet xuat tu dau tram co tac dung uc che virus cum H5N1
